.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 

.SS "template<class T>
.br
class Singleton< T >"A generic \fBSingleton\fP template class\&. 

This template provides a thread-safe and lazy-initialized singleton instance\&. The constructor and assignment operators are deleted to enforce a single instance\&.

.PP
\fBTemplate Parameters\fP
.RS 4
\fIT\fP The type of the singleton class\&. 
.RE
.PP

