.SS "template<class T> T * \fBSingleton\fP< T >::Instance ()\fR [inline]\fP, \fR [static]\fP"

.PP
Returns a pointer to the singleton instance\&. The instance is created the first time this method is called and destroyed automatically when the program terminates\&.

